Titolo: Disciples II: Dark Prophecy

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Disciples II: Dark Prophecy is a 2002 turn-based strategy game by Strategy First for Microsoft Windows. It is the sequel to the 1999 game Disciples: Sacred Lands, and has become significantly more successful in terms of both sales and popularity than its predecessor. A collector's edition version of the game was released, which included a card game based upon the story and five extra quests.
Four expansion packs were released: Guardians of the Light, Servants of the Dark, Rise of the Elves, and Gallean's Return. A port of Disciples II for the Nintendo DS was in development, but not released. A sequel named Disciples III: Renaissance was released in 2009.